imdb.plot outline: Small Fry, Free Range, and Uncle Wattles are an easy-going chicken trio who live on Funny Farm. Not far from the far, a giant junkyard is home to a pair of weasels known as Glutton and Slim. These old boys, when not at war with each other, raid the Farm with one hare-brained scheme after another in a luckless pursuit of the elusive chicken dinner.
